text: ‘How can you be so thankless to your best friend, Lizzie?
Been a knocking about with a pretty many tides, ain’t hepardner?
‘Couldn’t you, Gaffer?’‘No. Has a dead man any use for money?
Is it possible for a dead man tohave money?
What world does a dead man belong to?
How can money be a corpse’s?
Cana corpse own it, want it, spend it, claim it, miss it?
